cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper discusses cooperative deep multi-agent reinforcement learning, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on decentralised execution and communication constraints suggests a potential fit for multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the proposed MAVEN approach involves a hybridisation of value and policy-based methods, which could also be relevant to robotics (cs.RO) research.
